<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'
import { ref } from '@vue/reactivity';
export default {
  name: 'HomePage',
  props: [
    'loginCheck',
  ],
  setup(props) {
    let homeLoginCheck = ref(props.loginCheck)
    axios.get('/api/').then(res=>{
      console.log(res.data);
      if(res.data === 'already login') {
        props.loginCheck = ref(true);
      } else {
        props.loginCheck = ref(false);
      }
      
    })
    
  }
}
</script>
